.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REMOTE-BALANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-remote-balance \- show remote (inbound) balance across all channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-remote-balance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns inbound liquidity (remote balance) per channel and aggregated totals.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{total_remote_msat, total_capacity_msat,
 channels:[{channel_id, peer_id, remote_msat, total_msat}]}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-balance (1),
.BR lightning-liquidity-report (1)
